creator: C&A Marketing Inc.
descriptionHtml:
When you think instant, you think Polaroid.

Now when you think mobile wireless printing, you think Polaroid POP. Take your pictures from any mobile device and print them anytime, anywhere. Download the Polaroid POP app now and see all the amazing features this app has to offer.

Print pictures instantly from your smartphone or mobile device. Edit photos, add Frames, stickers, signature your memorable photos all from your Polaroid POP APP.

Features:

Edit Images:
Edit your photos with this amazing feature. Zoom, crop, tint and color your images for printing the perfect picture. Personalize your photos by adding frames, stickers, drawing and much more.

Sync Photos from Polaroid POP CAM:
Sync images of Polaroid POP CAM to your phone automatically or manually via Polaroid POP APP.

Print Images:
Print signed and unsigned pictures instantly from your smartphone and print multiple copies too.
descriptionShort: Edit Images, Sync images, Print pictures instantly from Polaroid POP.
